         <h2><a href="/news/2016/March/in-memoriam-father-angelico-valeriote-">In Memoriam: Father Angelico Valeriote </a></h2>
         
        <p style="border-top: 1px solid #fff; padding-top: 5px;">We regret to inform you that Father Angelico Valeriote, died on Thursday, March 10, 2016. Please pray that Father Angelico may rest in the peace of Christ and that his family may be consoled in their faith in Christ.                     <a href="/news/2016/March/in-memoriam-father-angelico-valeriote-" >[read&nbsp;more]</a>
                  </p>
        
