    </a>
      <div class="news">
        
        
                    
         <h2><a href="/news/2016/March/photos-160th-anniversary-mass">Photos: 160th Anniversary Mass</a></h2>
         
        <p style="border-top: 1px solid #fff; padding-top: 5px;">On <strong>Sunday, February 28th</strong>, the Diocese of Hamilton celebrated its 160th Anniversary at the Cathedral Basilica of Christ the King. The 11:00a.m. Mass hosted a variety of special guests, including His Grace, Archbishop Luigi Bonazzi, the Apostolic Nunzio of Canada, who preached at Mass during his first official visit to the Diocese. Also present was Dr. Kevin Smith, who was honoured as a Knight of St. Gregory.                    <a href="/news/2016/March/photos-160th-anniversary-mass" >[read&nbsp;more]</a>
                  </p>
        
      </div>
