      <div class="news">
        
        
                    
         <h2><a href="/mercy-in-action">Mercy In Action: St. Philippe, Burlington</a></h2>
         
        <p style="border-top: 1px solid #fff; padding-top: 5px;">Pope Francis calls us to "merciful like the Father" in this Year of Mercy. In our new <em><strong>Mercy in Action</strong></em> series, St. Philippe in Burlington shows us that a small parish can have a big heart!                    <a href="/mercy-in-action" >[read&nbsp;more]</a>
                  </p>
        
      </div>
