    <img src="/uploads/galleries/2016_riteofelection/riteofelection_web.jpg" alt="Photos: Rite of Election 2016" width="631" height="286"/>
    </a>
      <div class="news">
        
        
                    
         <h2><a href="/news/2016/February/photos-rite-of-election-2016">Photos: Rite of Election 2016</a></h2>
         
        <p style="border-top: 1px solid #fff; padding-top: 5px;">On <strong>Sunday, February 14th, 2016,</strong> the first Sunday of Lent, the Rite of Election was celebrated at both the Cathedral Basilica of Christ the King in Hamilton and the Basilica of Our Lady Immaculate in Guelph. A combined 120 catechumens from around the Diocese signed the Book of the Elect and acknowledged their preparation and intention to receive the Sacraments of Initiation at the Easter Vigil.                    <a href="/news/2016/February/photos-rite-of-election-2016" >[read&nbsp;more]</a>
                  </p>
        
