            <h2 style="margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0;"><a href="http://bit.ly/yrdoh" >Year of Mercy Youth Rally</a></h2>
         
            <p style="margin-top: 0; border-top: 1px solid #fff; padding-top: 5px;">Join us on <strong>Saturday, May 21st</strong> for our Year of Mercy Youth Rally! Together through prayer, sacrament and fellowship, let us celebrate the gift of Godâs mercy and welcome the opportunity to be the face and heart of Christâs mercy to the world.                             <a href="http://bit.ly/yrdoh">[read&nbsp;more]</a>
